<br>
As I told every AD officer I could find,  we are looking into Moehx's history.   Adell told needra that no proof would be provided.  No one would provide me even circumstantial evidence when I got back.  Fine. I began to conduct an investigation.  The next day,  AD attacked us.   I'm not sure how they expected us to conduct an investigation in that length of time.  <br>
<br>
We are continuing the investigation, and I'm sure guild will vote to remove him if it turns up it is him.  I don't like being lied to.<br>
<br>
However, we will not bend knee to any guild that comes making accusations of &quot;deguild this person now, or we will kill you,  and we won't back up our claims&quot;.  I know EXACTLY  what AD would say if I came at them like that.  But unfortunately the swear filter would not let me repeat it.  <br>
<br>
 We've been polite, and respectful both to those guilds ahead of, and below us.  Needra admitted she reacted harshly initially and that she was leading tough raid at the time, that was relayed to AD.  Thats a lot closer to an apology than we ever got from you when we were were spoken to in the same manner.<br>
<br>
